data.description: OPEN HOUSE THIS WEEKEND SATURDAY 13TH 11-3PM SUNDAY 14TH 12 - 3 PM. This beauty will not disappoint, tucked away in a small, secluded neighborhood, the Northern Heights subdivision. This adorable 2-bedroom 2-full bath home has an Open floor plan with High ceilings, Berber carpet with a Tile entry. Each Bedroom has its own Bathroom and walk-in-closet with closet organizers. Step outside on to your covered patio and enjoy your morning coffee or evening glass of wine while watching your favorite show or team on the outside TV. This home has been well maintained.
